

Yolo County Buyers Guide is a professional media publication created by Davis Life Magazine for Coldwell Banker Doug Arnold Real Estate, Inc. The magazine features stories about Davis, the real estate market, homes for sale, real estate agents, preferred vendors, etc. On the first of each month a new magazine is published. Visit the real estate sections to see listings, virtual tours, agent directories and open houses. The Yolo County Buyers Guide is another great media resource for Davis. You may sign up for a subscription at no cost by visiting http://www.yolocountybuyersguide.com their website.

